query:
/*+  */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from tag_question AS tq1
inner join question AS q1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.score >= 1 AND q1.score <= 10
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('academia',
'gaming',
'security',
'webapps',
'webmasters')
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('achievements',
'google-apps-script',
'hash',
'journals',
'league-of-legends',
'malware',
'masters',
'pokemon-go',
'research-process',
'thesis',
'url',
'xbox-360')
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND a1.question_id = q1.id
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.reputation >= 0 AND u1.reputation <= 10 group by t1.name;
